{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1677-07_074", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Sur le Jubilé de Son Altesse Royale"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Le Nouveau Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", juillet 1677 (tome V), p 74-80"}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/note[1]", "tag": "note", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/note[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Il existe une autre édition parisienne, réalisée \"Suivant la Copie imprimée\" par Guillaume de Luyne, dont la pagination diffère."}], "attributes": {"resp": "editor"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[2]", "text": "."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Dans le mesme temps que le Roy a fait éclater sa pieté par toutes ces magnificences, Monsieur a donné des marques publiques de la sienne, en venant gagner icy son Jubilé qu’il n’avoit pû gagner à l’Armée. Il a fait ses Stations avec un zele qui a édifié tout le monde. Cependant il s’est trouvé un Scrupuleux qui luy a donné quelque avis sur la préparation où ce grand Prince se devoit mettre pour une action si pieuse. Jugez, Madame, par la lecture de ces Vers, si le scrupule a deû l’arrester."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "SUR LE JUBILÉ "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[1]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "de "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]/lb[1]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]/text()[2]", "text": "Son Altesse Royale."}], "attributes": {"rend": "sc"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous pensez donc, Seigneur, gagner le Jubilé,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Sans reparer l’outrage & l’affront signalé,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " Que par une injustice étrange"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " Dont toute l’Europe a parlé,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " Vous fistes au Prince d’Orange"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": " Dans vostre dernier Démeslé ?"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[1]", "tag": "ab", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[1]/text()[1]", "text": "***"}], "attributes": {"type": "ornament"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Ne vous souvient-il plus avec quelle furie"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous fustes l’attaquer au milieu de ses Gens,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1