"i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " Mais à vous dire vray, Seigneur,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " Sa Morale est un peu severe,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " Et la chose pour un Vainqueur"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[5]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": " Est assez difficile à faire."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[5]", "tag": "ab", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[5]/text()[1]", "text": "***"}], "attributes": {"type": "ornament"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Jurez qu’estant vaincu dans quatre ou cinq Combats,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous quitterez aux Flamans la Campagne"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Que vous rendrez Saint Omer à l’Espagne,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Que vous soufrirez tout des Troupes d’Allemagne,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " Et cela fait, ne doutez pas"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[6]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Qu’on ne vous puisse absoudre de tout cas."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Ces Vers m’ont esté donnez comme estant du Pere Comire Jesuite, qui en fait si bien de Latins. C’est un Homme dont le merite est connu. Il n’en faut point d’autre preuve que la correspondance qu’il entretient avec tous les Sçavans, & l’estime particuliere qu’a pour luy Monsieur l’Evesque de Paderbon. Le sufrage de ce grand Prélat est un titre incontestable de gloire pour tous ceux à qui il croit qu’il soit juste de l’accorder."}]}]}